_From @codito on March 24, 2017 8:18_

In VS, the generated assemblyinfo has this header, static analysis tools skip it because of this header. Can such a header added in CLI build as well?

```
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// <auto-generated>
//     This code was generated by a tool.
//     Runtime Version:4.0.30319.42000
//
//     Changes to this file may cause incorrect behavior and will be lost if
//     the code is regenerated.
// </auto-generated>
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
```
